==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Milker
<hw>Milk"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
milks; also, a mechanical apparatus for milking cows.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A cow or other animal that gives milk.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Milkful</ent>⟦br⟧
